WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:22.980 --> 01:27.880
[Jiangzhou University]

01:52.850 --> 01:55.450
Just as Mumu described, campus life

01:55.620 --> 01:56.729
is vibrant and bustling.

01:57.650 --> 01:58.940
Rushing across the campus

01:58.940 --> 02:00.940
for lectures,

02:01.940 --> 02:04.300
sharing dorms with friends

02:04.690 --> 02:06.500
from all over the country,

02:07.620 --> 02:09.410
having dorm meetings every day,

02:09.690 --> 02:12.090
and discussing everything
from national issues to juicy gossip,

02:12.540 --> 02:14.580
from Calculus to Wall Street.

02:15.330 --> 02:17.260
Even though I only chime in
occasionally,

02:17.410 --> 02:18.130
I've already talked

02:18.130 --> 02:20.450
more than I ever did in high school.

02:28.329 --> 02:30.100
You took my picture without my consent.

02:30.460 --> 02:32.180
You have no evidence.

02:32.380 --> 02:33.490
Look at how revealing you're dressed.

02:33.660 --> 02:34.770
You're practically
showing off your body.

02:34.980 --> 02:36.850
Delete the picture, now.

02:37.100 --> 02:37.570
Are you insane?

02:37.570 --> 02:38.460
Delete the picture.

02:39.690 --> 02:40.290
What's going on?

02:40.290 --> 02:41.329
He took my picture.

02:41.460 --> 02:42.540
Who are you?

02:42.540 --> 02:43.460
Why did you do that?

02:43.620 --> 02:44.460
Delete the picture.

02:44.460 --> 02:45.130
Mind your own business.

02:45.130 --> 02:46.410
This is my business. Don't you leave.

02:46.410 --> 02:46.980
Don't leave.

02:46.980 --> 02:48.130
If not, I'll call security.

02:48.130 --> 02:48.980
What has happened, Qingyu?

02:48.980 --> 02:49.820
This guy took her picture.

02:51.050 --> 02:52.260
Call security now.

02:52.490 --> 02:53.930
Qingyu, let's just forget it.

02:54.620 --> 02:56.260
Delete it now.
Do you not want to graduate?

02:56.260 --> 02:57.540
Hello, security.

02:57.620 --> 02:59.380
Please come to the female dorm now.

02:59.380 --> 03:00.690
Don't be afraid. It's not your fault.

03:00.690 --> 03:01.410
Exactly.

03:01.900 --> 03:03.020
There's a pervert here.

03:03.980 --> 03:05.100
Fine, I'll delete it.

03:09.490 --> 03:10.380
Can I go now?

03:13.570 --> 03:14.570
Thank you so much.

03:14.900 --> 03:15.540
You should go back now.

03:18.260 --> 03:19.380
Let's go back to our dorm.

03:19.380 --> 03:20.570
This guy is unbelievable.

03:21.930 --> 03:22.740
What a pervert.

03:23.260 --> 03:23.980
Let's go.

03:27.660 --> 03:28.570
[Psychological Counselors Home]
This way, please.

03:29.570 --> 03:31.540
Aside from sorting out case files,

03:31.540 --> 03:33.060
another part of your job

03:33.170 --> 03:34.610
is receiving visitors.

03:35.130 --> 03:37.170
People visiting for the first time

03:37.170 --> 03:38.570
tend to feel nervous.

03:38.890 --> 03:39.850
Without a buffer,

03:39.850 --> 03:42.730
they might find it hard to relax,

03:43.100 --> 03:44.450
which isn't ideal

03:44.450 --> 03:46.570
for starting a therapy session.

03:47.410 --> 03:49.410
The reception desk is ahead there.

03:49.820 --> 03:52.010
After registering the visitors,

03:52.100 --> 03:55.060
you can try having a brief conversation
with them

03:55.980 --> 03:59.010
or show them the bookshelf over here,

03:59.010 --> 04:01.780
where they can find psychological books.

04:03.540 --> 04:05.570
You're majoring in finance,

04:05.890 --> 04:08.100
so why did you decide
to take a part-time job here?

04:09.170 --> 04:11.610
Well, my mother suffers from depression

04:11.610 --> 04:13.570
and is currently receiving treatment.

04:14.130 --> 04:16.540
During high school, my best friend and I

04:16.540 --> 04:18.500
also went through emotional struggles.

04:18.980 --> 04:20.130
It was Dr. Le Fan
from the provincial hospital

04:20.130 --> 04:21.660
who helped us through it.

04:22.380 --> 04:25.220
So I hope I can do my part

04:25.290 --> 04:27.730
to help people like my mother and me.

04:29.500 --> 04:31.850
In practical therapy sessions,

04:31.940 --> 04:33.130
there are

04:33.130 --> 04:35.380
some effective methods,

04:35.540 --> 04:37.340
like implosive therapy

04:37.340 --> 04:39.170
or sand play therapy.

04:39.540 --> 04:41.100
If you're interested,

04:41.100 --> 04:43.260
you can take the time
to learn more about them

04:43.260 --> 04:44.980
during your time here.

04:46.060 --> 04:49.010
Of course, these therapy techniques
are just tools.

04:49.500 --> 04:51.980
The most healing method

04:52.220 --> 04:53.409
is love.

04:54.220 --> 05:04.650
[Episode 23]
[Behind You, Always]

05:04.650 --> 05:08.020
[Huanzhou People's Hospital]

05:11.220 --> 05:11.850
I'll hold it for you.

05:11.850 --> 05:14.260
It's fine. I'm all good now.

05:15.170 --> 05:17.540
The doctor did say you should relax

05:17.540 --> 05:18.500
and go out for walks.

05:18.500 --> 05:19.260
Hmm.

05:20.500 --> 05:22.130
We've been here for a long time,

05:22.130 --> 05:23.500
non-stop busy,

05:23.820 --> 05:25.450
and none of us have been anywhere.

05:26.060 --> 05:27.410
There's a park nearby.

05:27.410 --> 05:28.500
Let's go there.

05:28.890 --> 05:29.660
Really?

05:29.980 --> 05:30.450
Sure.

05:31.980 --> 05:34.130
Take me to the park.

05:42.580 --> 05:44.050
This place

05:44.220 --> 05:46.490
is just three bus stops away
from Chaoyang Village.

05:47.930 --> 05:49.980
I didn't know

05:50.170 --> 05:52.170
there was a big park here.

05:52.730 --> 05:55.340
Mom, you had so many things
to worry about back then.

06:02.220 --> 06:03.610
I was worried about everything
for no reason, though.

06:05.610 --> 06:06.220
Let's go...

06:06.810 --> 06:07.050
This way.

06:07.050 --> 06:08.340
- This way.
- This way.

06:10.490 --> 06:14.610
You said your dorm-mate
lost all her money

06:14.610 --> 06:15.900
playing the stock market?

06:16.220 --> 06:17.020
Yeah.

06:17.170 --> 06:18.850
The funny thing
is that she used the method

06:18.850 --> 06:20.580
our securities lecturer taught.

06:20.580 --> 06:22.780
The lecturer then said she had bad luck.

06:22.900 --> 06:24.850
Back in my school days,

06:24.900 --> 06:26.460
we used to do part-time jobs

06:26.850 --> 06:28.340
like folding matchboxes

06:28.700 --> 06:31.020
or picking tea leaves
at a tea plantation.

06:31.850 --> 06:33.580
Young people these days
are something else.

06:33.730 --> 06:37.050
You study and run a business
at the same time.

06:39.290 --> 06:42.900
How's it going at the counseling firm?

06:43.220 --> 06:44.810
Is it tiring?

06:45.850 --> 06:47.020
It's pretty easy.

06:47.100 --> 06:49.250
I get to do something I like,

06:49.290 --> 06:50.700
learn new things,

06:51.100 --> 06:52.490
and even make some money.

06:52.490 --> 06:53.340
That's wonderful.

06:54.050 --> 06:54.980
Qingyu,

06:55.220 --> 06:56.730
it is already exhausting

06:57.050 --> 06:59.050
with all those lectures,

06:59.810 --> 07:01.340
and now you're doing a part-time job.

07:01.410 --> 07:03.100
Don't strain yourself.

07:03.810 --> 07:05.170
We're not short of money.

07:05.540 --> 07:07.250
Remember to keep it for yourself.

07:07.250 --> 07:08.810
There's no need to send money home.

07:11.170 --> 07:12.140
Close your eyes.

07:17.490 --> 07:18.850
I've got a gift for you.

07:27.700 --> 07:29.250
It's from the money you sent home.

07:29.980 --> 07:31.290
I didn't add any.

07:32.020 --> 07:33.100
Is it expensive?

07:33.580 --> 07:34.370
No.

07:35.340 --> 07:36.700
You're an adult now.

07:37.610 --> 07:40.220
Back then, everyone in high school
had phones.

07:40.460 --> 07:42.900
I could tell you also wanted one.

07:43.659 --> 07:46.220
But I was worried
you might get distracted.

07:48.409 --> 07:49.850
Now, you're an adult.

07:50.100 --> 07:51.490
You need your own phone.

07:51.780 --> 07:53.700
Remember to call me often.

07:58.730 --> 07:59.900
Look at them.

07:59.900 --> 08:01.050
Let's go shopping later.

08:01.290 --> 08:02.980
Doll yourself up a bit.

08:03.700 --> 08:05.540
Don't spend all your time studying.

08:05.580 --> 08:07.250
You should learn to dress up,

08:07.700 --> 08:08.490
right?

08:08.580 --> 08:10.580
Carry yourself like a young lady.

08:14.100 --> 08:14.660
Let's go.

08:20.280 --> 08:26.280
[Xingzhou]

08:32.100 --> 08:32.659
Mom.

08:32.809 --> 08:33.409
Yes?

08:33.659 --> 08:35.490
You gave me this pearly hair clip then.

08:35.490 --> 08:37.049
I should give it back to you.

08:37.049 --> 08:37.610
Sure.

08:37.610 --> 08:39.020
Put it in my room.

08:39.289 --> 08:40.289
Let me put it on for you.

08:40.580 --> 08:41.220
What?

08:41.220 --> 08:41.460
Here.

08:41.460 --> 08:42.580
You want to put it on for me?

08:42.659 --> 08:43.929
Don't move. Here.

08:46.700 --> 08:48.020
You look pretty with it on.

08:48.540 --> 08:49.250
Beautiful.

08:49.250 --> 08:50.220
Let's eat!

08:50.220 --> 08:50.850
All right.

08:51.220 --> 08:52.020
Come on.

08:54.370 --> 08:54.980
Come on.

09:00.540 --> 09:02.250
You all said you wanted a hotpot.

09:02.700 --> 09:04.140
These are your favorites.

09:09.490 --> 09:11.220
Should I give a toast?

09:11.220 --> 09:11.980
Go ahead.

09:12.290 --> 09:13.020
Go ahead.

09:13.020 --> 09:14.540
You go first.

09:16.250 --> 09:20.580
First of all, congratulations
on your mom's recovery and discharge.

09:21.220 --> 09:23.290
Also, may Qingyu

09:23.780 --> 09:25.540
do well in her studies in Jiangzhou.

09:25.980 --> 09:29.410
And cheers to us

09:29.460 --> 09:31.460
for moving into such a beautiful home.

09:32.700 --> 09:33.980
I'll say something too.

09:34.780 --> 09:37.850
May your dad's new job go well.

09:37.850 --> 09:38.930
♪Under the sunlight♪

09:38.930 --> 09:41.220
May Jinyu continue his studies,

09:41.220 --> 09:42.730
regardless of his grade.

09:43.330 --> 09:44.540
♪Raise me up, hold me high♪

09:44.540 --> 09:45.290
Hey, Mom.

09:45.290 --> 09:47.540
What kind of blessing is that?

09:47.700 --> 09:49.140
Anyway, our family

09:49.140 --> 09:50.370
will only get better.

09:50.370 --> 09:50.660
Yes.

09:50.660 --> 09:51.730
We'll get better.

09:51.730 --> 09:52.020
Cheers.

09:52.020 --> 09:56.300
♪During the dark night♪

09:56.300 --> 09:57.890
♪A guiding light♪

09:57.890 --> 09:58.610
Let's put some food in it.

09:58.610 --> 09:59.700
Let's start eating.

09:59.700 --> 10:00.340
Hmm.

10:00.340 --> 10:01.400
♪Just like you♪

10:01.400 --> 10:03.730
♪Makes life turn bright♪

10:03.730 --> 10:05.220
The mushrooms are big.

10:06.350 --> 10:11.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

10:11.180 --> 10:12.650
I want sugar.

10:12.700 --> 10:13.610
Oh.

10:13.700 --> 10:14.530
I forgot.

10:15.180 --> 10:15.980
Go and get it.

10:15.980 --> 10:17.010
Jeez.

10:17.010 --> 10:18.710
♪Running for truth♪

10:19.250 --> 10:21.010
I want the same sugar Dad got me.

10:21.010 --> 10:22.460
Sure, no problem.

10:23.750 --> 10:27.980
♪Drawing on the hope♪

10:27.980 --> 10:31.580
♪That you render me♪

10:32.250 --> 10:34.650
Dad, Mom,
Yu and I will give you a toast.

10:34.650 --> 10:35.340
Hmm.

10:36.010 --> 10:36.820
To Dad and Mom.

10:36.820 --> 10:37.530
Come on.

10:37.730 --> 10:38.650
Cheers!

11:09.300 --> 11:10.130
Are all the dishes here?

11:10.130 --> 11:10.460
Hmm.

11:16.100 --> 11:16.650
Qingyu.

11:16.650 --> 11:17.100
Hmm?

11:17.100 --> 11:18.060
You know what?

11:18.530 --> 11:19.820
That fellow Hei

11:20.220 --> 11:22.010
just got sentenced.

11:22.850 --> 11:23.460
Guo Hei,

11:23.890 --> 11:24.820
also known as Hei,

11:25.370 --> 11:27.180
gathered others
to cause public disturbances,

11:27.650 --> 11:29.340
assaulted individuals multiple times,

11:29.850 --> 11:32.420
vandalized and destroyed property,

11:32.850 --> 11:34.180
and threatened others,

11:34.650 --> 11:36.770
severely disrupting their livelihood,

11:37.370 --> 11:38.460
which is a serious crime.

11:38.820 --> 11:39.650
The People's Court

11:39.650 --> 11:40.810
hereby convict him of the crime

11:40.810 --> 11:42.940
of picking quarrels
and provoking trouble.

11:44.060 --> 11:45.490
In 2006,

11:45.490 --> 11:47.850
Guo Hei disseminated private information
about his former girlfriend, Qiao,

11:47.850 --> 11:50.100
including her HIV-positive status,

11:50.460 --> 11:51.650
on online platforms.

11:52.420 --> 11:54.530
This has led the victim to experience
severe online abuse,

11:54.530 --> 11:57.370
resulting in her suicide.

11:57.770 --> 11:58.850
He was detained for ten days

11:58.850 --> 12:01.580
by the public security authority.

12:02.300 --> 12:04.340
Due to his history of repeat offenses

12:04.530 --> 12:06.420
and lack of remorse,

12:06.420 --> 12:08.420
the People's Court imposed
a severe penalty.

12:08.610 --> 12:11.460
He has been sentenced
to two years in prison.

12:14.530 --> 12:15.580
He couldn't outrun the law.

12:16.340 --> 12:18.340
Finally, we've avenged Beiyu

12:18.490 --> 12:20.820
and Ming Sheng.

12:27.370 --> 12:28.180
By the way, Qingyu,

12:28.730 --> 12:31.940
did something happen
between you and Ming Sheng?

12:32.340 --> 12:33.370
What?

12:33.890 --> 12:36.980
That day, when Dad and I
were closing up the noodle house,

12:36.980 --> 12:38.100
he suddenly showed up.

12:47.610 --> 12:57.110
[Qiao's Handmade Noodle House]

13:14.820 --> 13:16.730
Sir, a bowl of noodles, please.

13:17.460 --> 13:19.980
We're closed.

13:21.060 --> 13:21.890
Ming Sheng?

13:27.890 --> 13:28.770
What would you like to eat?

13:30.010 --> 13:30.820
Stir-fried noodles.

13:31.490 --> 13:32.100
Okay.

13:37.010 --> 13:37.820
Sir,

13:38.460 --> 13:39.820
please give me more chili

13:41.610 --> 13:42.420
and sugar.

14:29.130 --> 14:29.980
Thank you.

14:31.610 --> 14:33.100
Why are you eating here so late?

14:34.940 --> 14:37.420
I'm leaving tomorrow.

14:38.730 --> 14:39.530
I see.

15:54.850 --> 15:56.300
I don't think people from Huanzhou

15:56.300 --> 15:57.980
can really handle spicy food.

15:57.980 --> 16:00.770
He was trying too hard
to impress but failed.

16:01.490 --> 16:02.730
What else did he say?

16:06.700 --> 16:09.490
I asked him if it was too spicy.

16:10.130 --> 16:13.340
At first, he nodded.

16:13.770 --> 16:16.300
He didn't feel like saying much.

16:17.610 --> 16:20.730
He then mumbled.

16:22.220 --> 16:23.370
I couldn't hear him.

16:28.460 --> 16:32.460
I think it was "unforgettable".

16:54.490 --> 16:55.300
Qingyu?

16:56.650 --> 16:57.340
Qingyu?

16:59.700 --> 17:01.300
What? It's nothing.

17:17.420 --> 17:18.530
Did you water my plant?

17:19.300 --> 17:21.099
I did.

17:21.700 --> 17:24.130
That's good, but don't do it again.

17:26.490 --> 17:29.010
Some plants are watered at nighttime.

17:29.010 --> 17:29.580
All right.

17:29.580 --> 17:30.220
Right.

17:30.890 --> 17:32.530
Do you remember this?

17:32.890 --> 17:34.490
When we first moved to Huanzhou,

17:34.820 --> 17:35.530
it was only this tall.

17:35.770 --> 17:36.890
You said it was dead.

17:36.890 --> 17:39.300
Look at it now, it's thriving.

17:40.980 --> 17:42.580
So don't worry too much.

17:43.180 --> 17:43.890
All right, got it.

17:43.890 --> 17:45.300
You cherish them very much.

17:45.300 --> 17:46.180
I'll leave them alone.

17:46.300 --> 17:47.580
Yes. Leave them alone.

17:48.580 --> 17:51.130
Now that the kids have grown up,

17:51.130 --> 17:54.770
we don't need to care too much
about them.

17:54.770 --> 17:57.820
When Yu finishes his NCEE,

17:58.180 --> 18:00.490
it'll just be the two of us at home.

18:00.610 --> 18:01.980
Won't that be easier?

18:04.130 --> 18:05.580
I remember

18:05.890 --> 18:07.770
you mentioned
you wanted to travel somewhere

18:07.770 --> 18:08.820
when we just got married.

18:09.220 --> 18:09.890
Oh, it's Yunnan.

18:09.890 --> 18:12.980
Was it Lijiang or Xishuangbanna?

18:13.340 --> 18:15.010
We've got time now.

18:15.010 --> 18:15.700
Come on.

18:16.300 --> 18:17.100
Here.

18:22.820 --> 18:24.100
Get the money prepared.

18:28.700 --> 18:30.220
How much did you drink?

18:35.050 --> 18:37.090
You've suffered a lot these years.

18:39.140 --> 18:41.010
Go to bed, okay?

18:43.660 --> 18:45.700
I assure you

18:45.700 --> 18:47.250
our life will get better.

18:48.700 --> 18:49.460
Everything will get better.

18:49.460 --> 18:51.330
Oh, it's so sweet. Here.

18:51.330 --> 18:52.380
You can have it.

18:52.380 --> 18:52.860
This is sweet.

18:53.620 --> 18:54.140
It's sweet.

18:55.250 --> 18:55.770
Really.

19:01.870 --> 19:05.600
[Jiangzhou University]

19:08.530 --> 19:10.620
Today's topic

19:10.620 --> 19:13.530
is a common literary device:

19:13.730 --> 19:15.420
using natural imagery to convey emotion.

19:15.900 --> 19:18.980
[Literary Device: using natural imagery]
The author describes the scenery

19:18.980 --> 19:21.330
[to convey emotion]
with strong emotions.

19:21.620 --> 19:23.290
They express their feelings or emotions

19:23.290 --> 19:26.860
through the scenery or the object.

19:27.220 --> 19:29.220
The scenery evokes feelings,
or vice versa,

19:29.220 --> 19:31.140
a natural blend of emotion and imagery.

19:31.660 --> 19:34.490
Here's an example. A great writer

19:34.490 --> 19:37.050
asked his students
to translate a short essay.

19:37.220 --> 19:39.900
A phrase
a man might utter involuntarily,

19:40.290 --> 19:42.490
while walking with a woman
under the moonlight:

19:42.860 --> 19:44.090
"I love you."

19:45.090 --> 19:47.250
Many students adopted

19:47.250 --> 19:48.530
a direct translation.

19:49.330 --> 19:52.250
However, this writer thought
it shouldn't be this way.

19:52.250 --> 19:53.660
It should be translated implicitly.

19:54.050 --> 19:55.460
Does anyone know

19:55.570 --> 19:57.570
how he translated it?

19:58.770 --> 20:00.420
Qiao Qingyu, give it a try.

20:01.010 --> 20:03.420
Ma'am, she might not
be able to answer that.

20:03.530 --> 20:05.570
Qiao Qingyu isn't much into romance.

20:09.900 --> 20:12.050
He thought a direct translation
lacked its essence.

20:12.140 --> 20:15.250
"I love you" should be translated
as "The moon is beautiful tonight."

20:16.180 --> 20:17.530
Subtle yet beautiful.

20:17.530 --> 20:18.700
Blending his affection

20:18.700 --> 20:20.460
into the moonlight that shines on them.

20:20.730 --> 20:22.140
Yes, well said.

20:22.140 --> 20:22.810
Please sit.

20:27.980 --> 20:28.900
Qiao Qingyu.

20:29.490 --> 20:31.140
The moon tonight

20:33.860 --> 20:34.700
is beautiful.

20:39.180 --> 20:40.140
Indeed.

20:41.730 --> 20:42.620
Let's go to sleep.

20:52.010 --> 20:52.940
Qiao Qingyu.

20:55.330 --> 20:56.660
The moon tonight

20:58.050 --> 20:59.220
is truly beautiful.

21:08.660 --> 21:10.090
How's my hair?

21:10.490 --> 21:12.050
You can do this. Go for it.

21:12.530 --> 21:13.250
Go, buddy.

21:13.250 --> 21:14.420
Go, buddy. You got this.

21:20.140 --> 21:20.980
Qiao Qingyu!

21:21.770 --> 21:22.660
Qiao Qingyu!

21:23.530 --> 21:25.530
The moon is beautiful tonight.

21:27.220 --> 21:28.810
Let's go check it out.

21:30.250 --> 21:31.090
Qiao Qingyu,

21:32.460 --> 21:34.620
the moon is beautiful tonight.

21:35.250 --> 21:36.620
Not this again?

21:36.900 --> 21:38.290
Qiao Qingyu said,

21:38.490 --> 21:40.220
"The moon is beautiful tonight.

21:40.570 --> 21:42.770
But it has nothing to do with you."

21:43.330 --> 21:44.900
That's too mean.

21:45.530 --> 21:46.460
It's all right, buddy.

21:46.460 --> 21:47.140
It's all right.

21:47.140 --> 21:49.010
It's all right. Don't be upset.

21:51.620 --> 21:52.420
Qingyu,

21:52.490 --> 21:54.140
do you know who the guy downstairs was?

21:54.220 --> 21:56.460
He's Chen Ziyun, the most handsome guy
from the graduate school.

21:56.460 --> 21:58.330
His dad is a professor
in our department.

21:58.570 --> 22:00.700
He's quite a good choice.

22:00.770 --> 22:02.290
Maybe you should give it a thought.

22:02.460 --> 22:03.570
I believe

22:03.730 --> 22:06.050
Qingyu has someone she likes.

22:06.290 --> 22:08.940
She's rejected so many guys.

22:08.940 --> 22:11.420
Or maybe she has a broken heart.

22:11.770 --> 22:13.290
Share your story with us, Qingyu.

22:13.290 --> 22:14.010
By the way,

22:14.010 --> 22:15.900
you always go to the lighthouse.

22:15.900 --> 22:17.530
Are you waiting for someone?

22:21.220 --> 22:22.220
Pretty girl,

22:22.700 --> 22:24.700
you're wasting your youth.

22:24.980 --> 22:26.460
Maybe you can ask her
to give you some of her admirers.

22:42.160 --> 22:42.890
[Sheng:]

22:42.890 --> 22:44.570
[Qiao Qingyu, good luck with the NCEE.
Those three wishes will come true!]

23:16.460 --> 23:17.140
Hi.

23:17.660 --> 23:18.460
Here's your coffee.

23:21.090 --> 23:22.730
There's something I need to tell you.

23:23.220 --> 23:24.570
Our cafe will be moving

23:24.570 --> 23:26.330
to Huancheng Road South soon.

23:26.660 --> 23:27.530
This is so sudden.

23:27.940 --> 23:28.940
We don't have a choice.

23:28.940 --> 23:30.860
This area will undergo renovation.

23:30.860 --> 23:32.380
Since you're our regular customer,

23:32.380 --> 23:33.860
I think I should tell you about it.

23:35.530 --> 23:37.620
I noticed you've been coming here

23:37.620 --> 23:39.290
once or twice every month
for the past six months.

23:40.660 --> 23:41.980
I remember you said

23:41.980 --> 23:43.380
you were waiting for someone, right?

23:47.420 --> 23:47.980
Hmm.

23:48.570 --> 23:50.290
I hope you get what you wish for.

23:50.860 --> 23:52.010
This is on me.

23:52.460 --> 23:53.010
Please enjoy.

24:15.770 --> 24:16.420
Qiao Qingyu.

24:17.180 --> 24:18.050
This is mine.

24:46.250 --> 24:47.570
Here you go, Ms. Wang.

24:49.180 --> 24:50.810
Don't make fun of me.

24:51.810 --> 24:54.420
I'm just an intern assistant

24:54.420 --> 24:56.330
here for an academic exchange
with my supervisor.

24:56.330 --> 24:58.090
I happened to have a chance
to catch up with you.

25:05.980 --> 25:07.220
It tastes like the old days.

25:09.380 --> 25:11.250
Do you still think about those days?

25:14.330 --> 25:15.380
I don't know.

25:16.940 --> 25:20.730
Back then, I'd always thought about

25:20.730 --> 25:22.220
when I could leave home

25:23.140 --> 25:25.330
and grow up.

25:27.050 --> 25:29.490
I used to worry about being 18,

25:29.770 --> 25:31.980
but now I worry about being 20.

25:33.700 --> 25:35.380
I remember when we were in high school,

25:35.730 --> 25:37.620
we always asked this question.

25:38.050 --> 25:39.810
Will things get better when we grow up?

25:40.940 --> 25:42.530
Then, I watched a movie.

25:42.700 --> 25:44.490
The girl asked an adult

25:44.490 --> 25:45.460
the same question,

25:46.140 --> 25:47.770
"Will things get better when I grow up?"

25:48.420 --> 25:49.570
And the adult said,

25:49.900 --> 25:52.180
"No, this is life."

25:54.290 --> 25:56.860
Right. This is life.

25:58.330 --> 25:59.380
But luckily,

25:59.380 --> 26:00.860
we've become stronger now.

26:01.290 --> 26:01.700
Hmm.

26:03.090 --> 26:04.620
Well, enough about worries
from the past.

26:04.620 --> 26:06.180
Let's talk about the present ones.

26:06.460 --> 26:07.380
Are your admirers

26:07.380 --> 26:09.900
all lined up from here
to the campus gate?

26:10.180 --> 26:11.490
Don't make fun of me.

26:11.490 --> 26:12.900
What about you?

26:13.770 --> 26:15.620
Me? I'm focused on work.

26:18.490 --> 26:19.530
Oh, right.

26:19.530 --> 26:20.860
Let me take you somewhere.

26:21.810 --> 26:22.460
Let's go.

26:36.660 --> 26:40.810
[Anna's Musical Path]

26:40.870 --> 26:45.410
[I hope your fan signing event
goes well, Ms. Anna. Ming Qiuxin.]

26:53.250 --> 26:53.860
Thank you.

27:01.900 --> 27:02.490
Thank you.

27:11.180 --> 27:12.250
Ms. Anna, may I shake your hand?

27:12.250 --> 27:13.010
Sure.

27:13.290 --> 27:13.940
Thank you, Ms. Anna.

27:13.940 --> 27:14.660
Thank you.

27:24.220 --> 27:25.900
That's Ming Sheng's mom.

27:29.140 --> 27:31.380
Mr. Ming gave me the tickets
for tonight.

27:32.730 --> 27:35.290
His mom probably knows
how Ming Sheng is doing right now.

27:36.810 --> 27:38.420
Ms. Anna, may I take a photo with you?

27:38.420 --> 27:39.180
Sure.

27:47.980 --> 27:50.900
Aren't you curious about Ming Sheng?

27:53.330 --> 27:54.530
It's pointless, even if I am.

27:54.620 --> 27:55.860
It's been so long.

28:00.140 --> 28:02.900
Do you really think

28:03.010 --> 28:04.810
that when he saved you from the blizzard

28:04.980 --> 28:06.380
and planned to run away with you,

28:06.530 --> 28:08.660
it was
just because you were his classmate?

28:15.770 --> 28:18.330
Growing up means

28:18.330 --> 28:19.770
accepting what you can't change

28:19.860 --> 28:22.700
and changing what you can't accept.

28:24.570 --> 28:26.980
I heard Ming Sheng had been helping

28:26.980 --> 28:29.220
his mom prepare for the concert.

28:29.940 --> 28:31.220
He's back.

28:55.700 --> 28:56.980
Thank you.

28:59.050 --> 29:02.050
Mumu, I won't join
the fan signing event.

29:02.090 --> 29:03.770
I have something to attend to,
and I got to go.

29:28.180 --> 29:28.980
Give it to me.

29:35.250 --> 29:35.570
Thank you.

29:41.180 --> 29:41.660
Thank you.

29:46.250 --> 29:46.770
Thank you.

30:02.250 --> 30:02.980
Are you happy?

30:02.980 --> 30:03.460
Hmm.

30:05.420 --> 30:06.940
Guess what wish I just made.

30:08.460 --> 30:09.660
What did you wish for?

30:09.660 --> 30:10.770
My first wish

30:10.980 --> 30:13.250
is to get into my dream university.

30:14.010 --> 30:15.140
My second wish

30:15.220 --> 30:16.250
is for my family

30:16.250 --> 30:18.010
to stay healthy and safe.

30:19.660 --> 30:20.490
What about the third one?

30:21.860 --> 30:23.860
It's a secret. I'm not telling you.

30:49.320 --> 30:53.920
[Qingyu: Will you come back to Huanzhou
for the Chinese New Year?]

31:00.050 --> 31:01.330
I still can't come around.

31:02.010 --> 31:03.980
We were together
after high school graduation.

31:04.860 --> 31:05.900
It's been four years.

31:07.250 --> 31:08.290
But he broke up with me

31:08.290 --> 31:10.010
upon graduation.

31:10.900 --> 31:11.490
I...

31:12.700 --> 31:14.180
I just can't get over him.

31:14.700 --> 31:16.050
I can't accept
that our four-year relationship

31:16.050 --> 31:17.220
is just gone.

31:19.530 --> 31:21.050
Let it out.

31:21.250 --> 31:23.090
You'll feel better.

31:28.730 --> 31:30.090
I called and texted him,

31:30.090 --> 31:31.380
but he ignored me.

31:32.940 --> 31:34.180
I feel like I can't do anything

31:34.290 --> 31:35.860
without him.

31:37.700 --> 31:41.330
Would you be able to let go
if it were you?

31:47.810 --> 31:49.770
Well, you don't have to let go.

31:51.090 --> 31:52.380
No matter how much we try,

31:52.730 --> 31:54.460
it's hard to leave the past behind.

31:55.180 --> 31:57.380
Because it's part
of our life experience.

31:58.860 --> 32:00.330
What we need to do now

32:00.380 --> 32:02.050
is to make good use of the past

32:02.050 --> 32:03.180
for the sake of our future.

32:04.250 --> 32:05.730
Let's consider those upsetting memories

32:06.180 --> 32:07.940
part of our experience.

32:08.660 --> 32:10.530
Even though there are regrets,

32:10.770 --> 32:12.570
I believe there are still nice moments

32:12.570 --> 32:13.940
between you two.

32:17.940 --> 32:18.730
All right.

32:20.220 --> 32:21.460
I'll think about it.

32:31.220 --> 32:33.680
[To Sheng: Will you come back
to Huanzhou for the Chinese New Year?]

32:41.460 --> 32:41.940
Come in please.

32:43.860 --> 32:44.660
Dr. He.

32:44.660 --> 32:44.980
Yes?

32:44.980 --> 32:46.570
Here's the information
about visitors from last month.

32:46.570 --> 32:47.700
I've confirmed it.

32:47.900 --> 32:49.180
I've also called to confirm

32:49.180 --> 32:50.940
all the appointments for next week.

32:52.010 --> 32:52.810
Qingyu,

32:53.140 --> 32:55.180
is your new semester starting soon?

32:55.860 --> 32:57.420
What's your plan afterward?

32:58.330 --> 32:59.730
If you're planning to quit,

32:59.940 --> 33:01.010
well, you see...

33:01.730 --> 33:02.980
I've made up my mind.

33:03.250 --> 33:04.900
I'd like to stay.

33:05.330 --> 33:07.180
I'm hoping to pursue
a master's degree in psychology.

33:07.490 --> 33:08.620
I'll go back to Nanqiao Village

33:08.620 --> 33:09.900
to provide counseling services

33:09.900 --> 33:11.180
for left-behind children.

33:11.900 --> 33:14.050
I welcome you if you want to stay.

33:14.420 --> 33:17.140
But finance is a popular major.

33:17.530 --> 33:19.980
Have you discussed this
with your family?

33:20.980 --> 33:22.420
I made this decision myself.

33:22.420 --> 33:23.530
My parents support me.

33:24.220 --> 33:24.900
That's good.

33:24.900 --> 33:26.010
Then, good luck with your exams.

33:26.090 --> 33:27.940
Let me know if you need anything.

33:40.700 --> 33:42.010
Hi, please have a look.

33:42.050 --> 33:42.860
Thank you.

33:42.940 --> 33:45.050
Fully furnished units on Heping Road,
right by the subways

33:45.330 --> 33:47.420
and a two-minute walk
to a shopping mall.

33:48.620 --> 33:50.220
Kindergartens and primary schools
are located nearby.

33:50.220 --> 33:50.940
Please have a look.

33:52.090 --> 33:53.140
Hi, please take a look.

33:53.810 --> 33:54.460
Thank you.

33:54.940 --> 33:56.330
Hi. Thank you.

34:07.980 --> 34:08.699
Thank you.

34:11.050 --> 34:12.290
Perhaps one day,

34:12.489 --> 34:14.530
we'll be grateful for past mistakes

34:14.570 --> 34:15.530
that helped us grow.

34:16.900 --> 34:17.699
Jinrui,

34:18.139 --> 34:19.179
I hope

34:20.179 --> 34:21.659
you'll visit Nanqiao Village
if there's a chance.

34:21.659 --> 34:22.570
Please refer to the business card below.

34:22.900 --> 34:24.179
Contact me if you need anything.

34:24.460 --> 34:25.330
Sure. Thank you.

34:31.530 --> 34:32.219
Qingyu.

34:33.530 --> 34:34.730
I failed Bei

34:34.900 --> 34:36.489
and your family.

34:36.489 --> 34:36.900
Hi.

34:37.380 --> 34:37.770
Hi.

34:37.770 --> 34:38.659
Please have a look.

34:39.530 --> 34:41.900
I hope we can all let go of the past

34:41.940 --> 34:43.620
and start over.

34:43.730 --> 34:45.219
Hi, please have a look.

34:54.219 --> 34:55.050
Qingyu.

34:56.980 --> 34:57.770
Here's your letter.

35:01.700 --> 35:03.810
[To Qiao Qingyu]
Seriously? A letter?

35:04.490 --> 35:06.860
Is the sender living in the Stone Age?

35:09.380 --> 35:12.240
[Mail To Future]

35:14.670 --> 35:15.770
[Sent from Huanzhou High School,]

35:15.770 --> 35:16.870
[Binjiang District, Huanzhou,
Jiangnan Province]

35:17.620 --> 35:18.330
Thank you.

35:18.620 --> 35:19.570
I'm off.

35:32.330 --> 35:36.200
♪Perhaps♪

35:36.700 --> 35:42.380
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

35:43.480 --> 35:48.880
♪Counting the distance that separates us♪

35:49.700 --> 35:53.720
♪A single step, and we'd be closer still♪

35:53.720 --> 35:55.480
[Mail To Future]

36:03.530 --> 36:04.490
What are you writing?

36:05.420 --> 36:06.210
It's a secret.

36:06.210 --> 36:10.100
♪Perhaps♪

36:10.770 --> 36:12.650
♪We were afraid of losing♪

36:12.650 --> 36:15.490
They say the person you like

36:16.530 --> 36:18.130
is like a lighthouse on the sea.

36:18.130 --> 36:19.460
♪That's why we were hesitant♪

36:19.460 --> 36:22.340
It pulls us out of the darkness.

36:23.900 --> 36:25.860
You can always see its light,

36:26.650 --> 36:28.490
but it's unreachable.

36:29.490 --> 36:31.690
Perhaps that's the meaning
of a lighthouse.

36:32.330 --> 36:34.490
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

36:34.490 --> 36:37.130
There's always a lighthouse
shining just for me.

36:38.010 --> 36:41.680
♪Is your name♪

36:42.160 --> 36:47.380
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

36:48.130 --> 36:51.090
It's witnessed
countless separations and reunions.

36:52.980 --> 36:54.690
I strongly believe in

36:55.010 --> 36:56.980
the legend about the lighthouse.

36:56.980 --> 37:02.110
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

37:02.650 --> 37:06.440
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

37:06.920 --> 37:10.950
♪Is a place♪

37:11.370 --> 37:16.660
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

37:17.420 --> 37:20.690
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

37:21.240 --> 37:24.420
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

37:25.740 --> 37:27.940
But now is the toughest,

37:27.940 --> 37:29.010
the loneliest time in my life.

37:29.530 --> 37:31.010
You're the only one by my side.

37:32.090 --> 37:33.050
This is a thank-you.

37:35.090 --> 37:38.130
All right. I'll take it.

37:40.980 --> 37:41.900
Well...

37:42.940 --> 37:44.210
This will be a token between us.

38:22.740 --> 38:24.390
[Sheng]

38:24.390 --> 38:28.260
♪Perhaps♪

38:28.760 --> 38:34.440
♪Our thoughts form a bond♪

38:35.540 --> 38:40.940
♪The more we cross paths♪

38:41.760 --> 38:47.540
♪The more we begin to care♪

38:53.080 --> 38:56.960
♪In the future♪

38:57.640 --> 39:03.190
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

39:04.340 --> 39:09.840
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

39:10.870 --> 39:16.310
♪That never expires♪

39:28.090 --> 39:29.530
I heard you were looking for me.

39:43.420 --> 39:44.940
I came back here before the vacation.

39:46.420 --> 39:48.820
I'm not leaving this time.

39:51.420 --> 39:52.010
Hmm.

39:54.490 --> 39:55.260
Just "hmm"?

39:58.260 --> 39:59.050
Qiao Qingyu,

39:59.650 --> 40:01.380
there's something
I really wanted to ask you.

40:02.740 --> 40:04.900
When we were in Grade 3,

40:05.130 --> 40:06.530
I celebrated your birthday here,

40:07.090 --> 40:08.210
and you made your three wishes.

40:09.740 --> 40:11.570
So, what's the last wish you made?

40:12.860 --> 40:14.050
You don't have to know,

40:15.260 --> 40:16.610
because it has come true.

40:32.570 --> 40:33.690
You gave me this.

40:34.170 --> 40:36.210
You said this is your lucky charm,

40:36.420 --> 40:37.490
which brings you good luck.

40:38.940 --> 40:40.980
Now, I'm returning it to you

40:42.900 --> 40:44.380
because I'm lucky enough.

40:54.460 --> 40:59.290
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

41:00.140 --> 41:03.810
♪Is your name♪

41:04.290 --> 41:09.510
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

41:10.210 --> 41:13.640
♪At first sight♪

41:14.210 --> 41:17.360
♪The future has been determined♪

41:18.220 --> 41:24.320
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

41:24.780 --> 41:28.570
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

41:29.050 --> 41:33.080
♪Is a place♪

41:33.500 --> 41:38.790
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

41:39.550 --> 41:42.820
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

41:43.370 --> 41:46.550
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

41:48.530 --> 41:49.490
I told you.

41:49.490 --> 41:51.820
♪Only then does time
not betray our acquaintance♪

41:51.820 --> 41:52.820
As long as you turn around,

41:54.300 --> 41:55.260
I'll always be there.

42:10.900 --> 42:13.460
They say the person you like

42:13.460 --> 42:15.380
is a lighthouse
forever illuminating on the sea.

42:16.530 --> 42:19.820
It's a promise,
persistence amidst struggles,

42:20.420 --> 42:23.780
and light and hope in the darkness.

42:24.860 --> 42:26.860
Every day, it guides you

42:26.860 --> 42:28.570
toward where true love is.

42:29.980 --> 42:31.690
Even after all the paths I've taken,

42:32.210 --> 42:34.090
they still lead me to you.

42:35.090 --> 42:37.690
I strongly believe in
the legend of the lighthouse:

42:38.820 --> 42:40.610
People who part beneath it

42:41.050 --> 42:45.250
will reunite there.

42:45.950 --> 42:52.940
[The End]

43:21.520 --> 43:25.210
♪Perhaps♪

43:25.720 --> 43:31.420
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

43:32.560 --> 43:37.960
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

43:38.960 --> 43:44.520
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

43:50.190 --> 43:53.860
♪In the future♪

43:54.320 --> 44:00.040
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

44:01.540 --> 44:06.610
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

44:07.860 --> 44:13.020
♪That never expires♪

44:16.620 --> 44:21.090
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

44:22.090 --> 44:25.760
♪Is your name♪

44:26.260 --> 44:31.360
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

44:32.440 --> 44:35.660
♪At first sight♪

44:36.090 --> 44:39.370
♪The future has been determined♪

44:40.060 --> 44:45.620
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

44:46.720 --> 44:50.260
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

44:50.720 --> 44:54.660
♪Is a place♪

44:54.960 --> 45:00.520
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

45:01.190 --> 45:04.560
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

45:04.890 --> 45:08.360
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

45:08.890 --> 45:14.960
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
